cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with building a conversational agent and proposes a deep learning architecture for the same. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with developing an AI-based conversational agent. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a deep learning architecture for learning unified embeddings. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper proposes a neural network-based architecture. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper incorporates external knowledge through a Knowledge Base for the retrieval-based conversational agent.
